      <description>
        <![CDATA[
          <h2>KBLock 1.0.0</h2>
          <p>Initial public release.</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Global lock</strong> — Pin to one input source system-wide</li>
            <li><strong>Per-app rules</strong> — Auto-lock to a specific source per application</li>
            <li><strong>Smart suggestions</strong> — Learns your usage and suggests rules</li>
            <li><strong>iCloud sync</strong> — Your rules synced across all your Macs</li>
            <li><strong>Usage statistics</strong> — See how much you use each input source</li>
            <li><strong>Multi-language</strong> — Supports English, 中文, 日本語, 한국어</li>
          </ul>
        ]]>
      </description>
